<section id="files" class="doc-section">
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3><code>Seed document/</code></h3>
    <p>A folder containing the basic files needed to start document work. To compile <code>Seed document.tex</code> successfully, install the <code>bookmark</code> and <code>enumitem</code> packages. Refer to <a class="text-link" href="/section-1/installation/">Section 1.1</a>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3><code>Check document.tex</code></h3>
    <p>If this file compiles without errors, your installation is complete. Compiling is covered in <a class="text-link" href="/section-2/">Section 2.1</a>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3><code>keybindings.json</code></h3>
    <p>Keyboard shortcut configuration file. Covered in Section 2.1.1.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3><code>latex.json</code></h3>
    <p>Basic user snippets file. User Snippets are covered in Section 2.1.5.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="info-card">
    <h3><code>settings.json</code></h3>
    <p>VS Code settings configuration file. Covered in Section 2.1.1.</p>
  </div>
</section>
